data.description: Move right in to this fully remodeled 3 bedroom (with option to make it into 4) 2.5 bath townhouse style condominium! Full kitchen remodel featuring stainless steel appliance package, new plumbing fixtures, modernized cabinets and countertops, and an extra large center island! All THREE bathrooms have been remodeled with new fixtures, flooring, and modern accents! FULL REC room that has BRAND NEW CARPETING and would make a perfect 4th bedroom option, extra living space, or den area! Upstairs features 3 HUGE bedrooms that have cathedral ceilings! Master bedroom features an extra large walk in closet, and an ensuite! Furnace and water heater are BRAND NEW! Entire unit has been freshly painted and features brand new flooring and light fixtures throughout! Move right in, immediate occupancy!
